{"tid":872721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來尋晚華dee輸到就黎瀨屎","createTime":"2018-10-23T02:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T14:28:59.000Z","uid":92376,"like":151,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7c59164ce487841f385a241198032a6f5a497a4f","tid":872721,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=xxb5AzGlMsE1Na28VbEcx8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8e25a852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周一李斯特城作客阿仙奴被反勝1:3，主將占美華迪在完場前數分鐘忽然離場，衝入球員通道，直至完場也不見他的蹤影，難免引起球迷的揣測。<br />\n<br />\n戰至87比分鐘，當時李城落後1:3，球隊3個換人名額已經用完，占美華迪（Jamie Vardy）忽然一支箭似的跑回更衣室，令球隊在最後階段少打1人，賽後領隊佩爾解畫：「當時華迪有點不舒服，不能返回球場，現在看來沒事了。」<br />\n<br />\n華迪似乎是腸胃不適要急上厠所，至少賽後很多球迷都是這樣想，一名球迷在twitter上老實不客氣地問：「華迪真的在一場電視直播的比賽裡中途離場去開大？」<br />\n<br />\n在球場上人有三急時有發生，英格蘭名宿連尼加就表示在1990年意大利世界盃一場賽事中，他明明肚痛卻在場上強忍，結果在一次攔截後失禁，弄得十分狼狽，相比之下華迪及時衝入厠所解決大事，算是當機立斷。<br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34442c462e685166ec45ad96c5bc21ce76d34ca7","tid":872721,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"華DEE去轟啦"},{"pid":"a61a86d2a6f39355e4a08f9f9a65d25715b9088c","tid":872721,"uid":1275,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"上年拉莫斯有一場又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b190a9a7e501a09b82369cf067225ca7ebc4daf","tid":872721,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34442c462e685166ec45ad96c5bc21ce76d34ca7","tid":872721,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"華DEE去轟啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"老啦算啦"},{"pid":"3917206110ba644eaedac424d5e2bd45892bf99d","tid":872721,"uid":92376,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"a61a86d2a6f39355e4a08f9f9a65d25715b9088c","tid":872721,"uid":1275,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"上年拉莫斯有一場又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"輸到驚真係會肚屙<br />\n今年美麗蛇咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b183f89085483942eec9128dd2b54d2e37f22bf","tid":872721,"uid":67252,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"一名球迷在twitter上老實不客氣地問：「華迪真的在一場電視直播的比賽裡中途離場去開大？」<br />\n<br />\n急屎都唔屙得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca923b9f848b58fb317f441382f3eb7fb8b698e8","tid":872721,"uid":12034,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"見到我廠又十幾連勝 嚇到瀨屎正常既"},{"pid":"c1bb65ce1651e76d091c648c91390f821e517933","tid":872721,"uid":106426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4017b03796ff83b01e35c737007100666a7261ba","tid":872721,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca923b9f848b58fb317f441382f3eb7fb8b698e8","tid":872721,"uid":12034,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"見到我廠又十幾連勝 嚇到瀨屎正常既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"又或者又輸一場離逼走教頭又近一步而開心到瀨屎"},{"pid":"5303bc11842841dacdcbd99ee5208f8131fdd2eb","tid":872721,"uid":92376,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"在球場上人有三急時有發生，英格蘭名宿連尼加就表示在1990年意大利世界盃一場賽事中，他明明肚痛卻在場上強忍，結果在一次攔截後失禁，弄得十分狼狽<